{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act34side", "eventName": "生路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "BP-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "評議式迎接", "storyInfo": "艾麗妮跟隨海巡隊指揮官西昆妲調查資料分析師失蹤的真相。歌蕾蒂婭就深海獵人的種種異常接受評議會的質詢，眾人齊聚鬥智場，烏爾比安悄然出現在博士身側。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g11_aegirroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這段時間，都沒人進來過嗎？", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "房間內小幫手的中控元件也確認過了，沒有發現被篡改過的痕跡。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，請問這裡這個記錄要怎麼查看？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給她開啟權限。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，謝謝你！", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西昆妲取下了腰間掛著的裝置。她的筆尖飛舞，彷彿水藻般糾纏不清的線條不斷地在裝置的表面浮現。"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的指揮官這是在？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寫寫畫畫有助於她快速思考，這是西昆妲的習慣，聽說她還是研究員的時候就這樣。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旁人理解不了，上面也沒記什麼關鍵詞，全是一些只有她自己才能看懂的……呃，抽象畫。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（書籍按照薄厚的順序排列，貝殼裝飾物按照大小順序擺放，從鬥智場下載的所有資料則根據時間進行了歸類。）", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（浮藻脂質霜劑，能有效防止皮膚乾燥脫水，是因為彌利亞留姆要靠近海岸？）", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這個份量，幾乎夠用三年。）", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（一名普通的阿戈爾女性。謹慎，甚至有些膽小和刻板，與發展規劃所提供的資料相符。）", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那些微型水培箱——）", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些箱子是幹什麼用的？明明都空了，卻還掛在牆上？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。水培箱應該是切入點。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對房間裡所有與植物栽培相關的設備進行掃描。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，從圖利婭的檔案裡調取相關的資料，她或許有這方面的愛好。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scan", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖利婭曾就職於生態藝術創作所，主要負責瀕危深海藻類的培育。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據生態藝術創作所的資料……", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經過藝術家的精心培育，這些深海藻類能夠在生長的過程中相互交織，組成一幅不斷反映著生命進程的、動態的畫。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些微型水培箱是圖利婭的個人資產，這裡有她當時的作品影像。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很漂亮。", "name": "西昆妲＆艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "西昆妲＆艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這些水培箱看起來已經空置了很長時間。", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "檔案剛剛提到，圖利婭是在調職後才加入到航道計劃。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是因為某些原因放棄了過去的生活嗎？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。她的失蹤很可能與職業生涯的變故有關。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "掃描結果怎麼樣？", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各類植物栽培設備並無異常，但我們在房間的整合終端上發現了一份操作記錄。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "圖利婭在失蹤前兩天，從信標塔中控室下載過一份資料，並在自己的房間內製作了一份備份。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們在房間內並沒有發現它。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "追蹤她的行程，同時聯繫中控室，從他們那邊的下載記錄去追溯資料內容。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4009_irene_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她在失蹤前還能正常地在工作場所與住所之間往來，那她的同僚或親友也許對她的行為有所了解？", "name": "艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對主要社會關係的問詢安排好了嗎？報案人呢？", "name": "西昆妲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1391_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經安排妥當，很快就可以與她們會面。", "name": "海巡隊隊員"}, "figure_art": "avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.12, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.15, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g6_aegirarena", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "x": 60.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬迪，有什麼我能幫到你的嗎？", "name": "阿維圖斯"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我腦袋裡問題太多，有點不知道……", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這棵……金屬的“樹”？我只要對它提問就好了嗎？我小時候也聽過古樹保管知識的傳說，但我從沒見過這樣的……", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被你稱作“樹”的珊瑚狀裝置是一個巨型整合終端，它是阿戈爾千百年來知識與文化的結晶。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的所想、所知、所作、所賞，乃至許多仍待解答的問題，都儲存在這裡。它構成了鬥智場的核心。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "51_g6_aegirarena", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，鬥智場究竟是……", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最早由偉大的人類學家暨先史文明研究者瑪利圖斯提出創意並主持修建的公共設施，對整個國家都影響深遠的偉大設計。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了海面上互相支撐的環礁城市群和海溝下結構性的城市網路，我們的其他城市大多形態各異，很少有風格相近的設計。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但許多城市都不約而同地採納了瑪利圖斯的設計，設立了自己的鬥智場。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看周圍的人，他們在此思考、質疑、辯論，最後取得理解，做出決定。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最複雜的公式，最古老的圖紙，最優美的詩歌……還有最適合的道路，都在這裡誕生。這正是瑪利圖斯希望看到的景象吧。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您一直在提的瑪利圖斯……那是個怎樣的人？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要細數他為阿戈爾做出的所有貢獻，恐怕一整天的時間也不夠用。不過除此之外，我倒是還了解一些他的性格特質。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您認得他？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有沒有，瑪利圖斯生活在兩百多年前，早在我出生之前，他就已經從阿戈爾消失了。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#3$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，他的怪脾氣是我們學科的導師們津津樂道的話題。瑪利圖斯的理論推演能力極為出眾，卻很不喜歡自己得出結論。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在別人看來已經確鑿無疑的事情，他也還要與自己辯論良久，才願意得出結論。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人認為他是過於在意事物的價值與意義，才會陷入這無休止的辯論，但這不正是我們身為人類的天性？", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正因如此，他才主持修建了鬥智場。事實證明，我們確實需要一個隨時能讓我們與自己、與他人展開思辨的場所。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有什麼可以用來辯論的觀念，阿維圖斯先生……但我確實還有很多問題。我是該問您，問我自己，還是問這台終端？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_microrobot", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1401_1#1$1", "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.3}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "“小幫手”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，我們的小討論得暫時讓步於一場更大的交鋒了。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡接下來要進行一場重要的評議會，和你那三位同行者相關。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海獵人？！", "name": "喬迪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1380_1#5$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，我是不是看見了我們迷茫的陸地朋友？他在一臉緊張地為我們擔心呢。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（招手）", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#5"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隔得太遠了，他很難注意到。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但已經有其他人朝這邊看過來了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#5"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場評議會引起了過多計劃外的關注。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海獵人原本就足夠引人注目了，“死而復生”又讓故事平添了許多波折……", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論我們意願如何，“深海獵人”都已經是這個舞台上的主角了。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鯊魚，這場評議會是我們最後的“檢查”了吧？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我已經有些厭煩了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "幽靈鯊，你的狀態還好嗎？;斯卡蒂，別著急。;這麼大陣仗，就當歡迎儀式吧。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line188", "option2": "line188", "option3": "line188"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海獵人需要保持低調。但是博士，你我也需要謹慎行事。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "羅德島的處境總是這麼微妙。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line194"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。這一次，我們不僅是在兩個國家之間斡旋，更是在海洋與陸地之間，在兩種文明之間斡旋。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來我會短暫地離開你們，為歌蕾蒂婭策應。會議結束後，我將正式與阿戈爾的執政官接觸，以求海陸合作能夠達成。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，這座城市和我們所面對的局勢都還不明朗。身處關注的焦點，有些事情我很難放開手腳去做。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "但很少有人會關注你帶來的“小助理”。;所以應該由我來見機行事，對吧？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line202", "option2": "line202"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。務必注意行事方式，我不希望在與執政官談判的時候，需要臨時更換任務目標。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_003_kalts_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，凱爾希醫生在有些話題上總是格外依賴修辭藝術，不是嗎？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繞來繞去的，她不是一直都這樣講話？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的醫生啊，總是在考慮太多的東西，卻不善於表達自己的關心。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你是不是也覺得，阿戈爾更加直率的溝通方式，更方便我們互相了解？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "同意。;凱爾希有她的考量。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line219", "option2": "line219"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我和鯊魚可以保護好你。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，二隊長怎麼還沒來？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她應該會和克萊門莎執政官一起出現。畢竟，今天需要站在正中央的人，其實是她。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個，請問，您是勞倫緹娜小姐嗎？", "name": "熱情的阿戈爾人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "group_interclude_vertical_common", "size": "290,760", "style": 0.0, "switch": "true", "offset": "250,0", "channel": 3.0, "tsfrom": "0,1", "tsto": "1,1", "tsduration": 0.5}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true", "pfrom": "235,0", "pto": "235,0", "name": "avg_npc_1393_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顧問，您果然在這裡。", "name": "疲憊的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這批環境樣本的檢測結果已經出來了，需要您過目一下，判斷是否需要臨時補充一輪新的基因檢測。", "name": "疲憊的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，抱歉……你發了訊息，但我沒有注意終端。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#4$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您似乎很關心深海獵人的這場評議會。", "name": "疲憊的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得您原來在深海獵人研究所工作過？", "name": "疲憊的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒寧願不提那份工作。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過是的，我在那研究基因嵌合的方式，嘗試為深海獵人找到更安全、更有效的改造方案。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不喜歡深海獵人計劃？", "name": "疲憊的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個付出了慘痛的犧牲，卻沒取得什麼像樣成果的失敗計劃罷了，談不上什麼喜歡不喜歡。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#3$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過歌蕾蒂婭她們還活著，這是最重要的。就算為了她們幾個，我也得來。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們關係很好？", "name": "疲憊的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈。要是歌蕾蒂婭也這麼覺得就好了。", "name": "布蘭都斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1381_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿維圖斯老師，我能坐您旁邊嗎？", "name": "阿戈爾女性"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然了，卡西婭。小心點，你剛接受過胚胎分離手術，還需要恢復。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位是來自伊比利亞的客人，喬迪。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。你好。", "name": "卡西婭"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1380_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，您，您好。", "name": "喬迪"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿維圖斯老師，今天的參加者是不是太多了點？", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#4$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三個月前設施管理所也因為城市單元骨架的改造進行過一次評議，但關聯單位只有兩個。", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#4$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟評議會是嚴格以解決問題為重點的，只有問題複雜到單一部門無法解決，才會讓間接相關的部門也參與進來。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1387_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可現在鬥智場已經坐了快一半人，深海獵人的回歸，真的會有這麼大的影響嗎？", "name": "卡西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1387_1#5$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一項經過近兩百年的爭論才實際啟動的計劃……它的理念幾乎動搖了阿戈爾的根基，它的動向同樣牽動著阿戈爾的命脈。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#2$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "況且，航道計劃已經進行到了最關鍵的階段，任何預期之外的情況都值得關注。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅靠垂直上報注定無法得到周全的結論，克萊門莎執政官需要聽取更多領域的專業判斷。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，現場應該還有很多人是自發前來旁聽的。在這個敏感的時間點上，三位獵人的回歸，或許會讓許多人感到不安。", "name": "阿維圖斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1386_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和這場評議會沒有直接的關係，只是聽說您可能會出席……", "name": "熱情的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，抱歉。", "name": "熱情的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫盧契拉，曾經和您的父母有過一面之緣！", "name": "熱情的阿戈爾人"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "標尺、墨水……你在這座城市的穹頂系統工作？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我去年剛剛從那裡調離，不過還在設施管理所，在地面負責城市單元骨架的檢修和洋流測繪。", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不要去羨慕太陽，我們給予自身永恆的群星和無限的海洋。”", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很小的時候，公共養育所的撫養人帶我們在這裡進行過一次演出。", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們設想將微型光學機械編製成矩陣，用光點的明暗變化，將人思考時的神經活動以美觀的方式呈現出來。", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家排練了很久。但演出當天，鬥智場罕見地出現了故障，整個場地一瞬間暗了下去，只有那些小機器閃著光。", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時觀眾裡有對很般配的叔叔阿姨，他們變了個魔術——一條條光帶憑空垂落在鬥智場，穹頂伸出鬚腕，邀我們的小機器一同起舞。", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切是那麼美輪美奐，場地的故障反而顯得像是精心安排的……", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能想像那兩個傢伙得意的神情了。說不定，所謂的故障還真的應該算到他們頭上。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到發展規劃所進行職業評估時，我幾乎毫不猶豫地填報了穹頂系統。直到那時候我才知道，他們是很有名的穹頂設計師。", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……後來我就沒有再見過他們。", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們啟發了你，一面之緣，恰如其分。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，你剛剛說自己變更了職務。既然你已經和我們頭頂這透明的巨構結下了緣分，為什麼……", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧契拉！評議會快開始了，你要坐在這邊嗎？", "name": "卡西婭"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4079_haini_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，勞倫緹娜小姐，我的同事在叫我——歡迎回家，祝你們順利。", "name": "盧契拉"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "幽靈鯊"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該來的人差不多都到齊了……", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#6"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，博士，你要去哪？", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#6"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "深海獵人太引人注目了。;只是不想被各種人盯著看，不用管我。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line372", "option2": "line372"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_263_skadi#3"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，你還真是聽凱爾希的話。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#3"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_higheldshosfts", "volume": 0.4, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信各位已經知道，彌利亞留姆近日成功與伊比利亞方面建立聯繫。這意味著航道計劃即將進入最為關鍵的階段……", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一縷光紋從龐大的珊瑚狀終端脫離，環繞著克萊門莎，在空氣中連接成輕盈的環，隨著執政官的話語而舞動。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光紋交織成城市與浪潮、獵人與海嗣，言語被轉化成可視的影像，聲音在這一刻獲得了紋理。"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛還在喧囂的人群，轉瞬間便安靜下來。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1382_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "值此關鍵時刻，歌蕾蒂婭、斯卡蒂、勞倫緹娜，三位倖存的深海獵人順利返回了阿戈爾。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們的體檢結果，以及歌蕾蒂婭提交的任務報告已經上傳至鬥智場的終端，相信諸位已經自行查閱過了。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就其中的種種異常狀況……", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海獵人總戰爭設計師之一，阿戈爾榮譽軍團長，歌蕾蒂婭執政官將在此接受諸位的質詢。", "name": "克萊門莎"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你越過幾排阿戈爾人，找到一個相對靠後的位置，坐了下來。從這裡看過去，鬥智場中發生的一切盡收眼底，座位周圍也沒那麼擁擠。"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "評議會已經開始，偌大的環形建築，沒有人高聲說話，但每個人的發言都無比清晰。歌蕾蒂婭站在場中，所有人的目光都投注在她身上。"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很輕的腳步聲，幾不可聞。彷彿幽邃的穹頂在你身側投下了一塊陰影。"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要聲張。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則我會掐斷你的喉嚨。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line422"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}